# Counters definitions
###
Counter
  Name          enumi
End

Counter
  Name          enumii
  Within        enumi
End

Counter
  Name          enumiii
  Within        enumii
End

Counter
  Name          enumiv
  Within        enumiii
End

Counter
  Name          bibitem
End

Counter
  Name          figure
End

Counter
  Name          table
End

Counter
  Name          algorithm
End
